// This is a straming section file. Streaming sections are resposible for
// keeping everything in memory that needs to be there while the player is
// located within a given region of the level. This data is not only asset
// data (driven by GSA files), but also lighting and other types of data.
//
// Each line of the section file is another GSA that needs to be loaded
// by the scene loader and processed.

Environments/_Test/SH_TestMap.gsa 